Achievement! Top 50 in Kode Indonesia Challange

Programming Contest by Kalibrr Indonesia - 26 Oct 2017

Around October, 2-3 weeks before the Grand Final, I found free Programming Contest and joined the online round. After the online round finished, I got a mail to join the Grand Final as Top 50 Finalist. On D-1, all finalist invited to dinner. I met with friends from Jollybee Binus Team there.
Here is a photo with "Kevin Sogo", formerly 2nd winner of Google Code Jam.

This is the Grand Final of Kode Indonesia 2017.

This is the last scoreboard I got from the website. I think 31st place is not bad for not-so-routine competitive programmer like me. It was a great experience.
Sometimes I play in HackerRank or Codeforces for fun.

Parttime Backend Engineer

Ralali.com - Nov 2017 to Feb 2018

So, I got the chance to Part Time at Ralali.com as Backend Developer. I learnt many things that is different from previous company.

Become Fulltime Software Engineer

Ralali.com - Mar 2018 to Feb 2019

First fulltime experience as Backend Developer. Here is photo of my birthday on January 2019.

Graduation

Binus University - 12 Dec 2018

I got the title: S.Kom., S.Si (Sarjana Komputer & Sarjana Sains)

Life as Lead Engineer at Ralali.com

Ralali.com - Mar 2019 to Jan 2020

First team: GRIFFIN, handle initiation of Finance Product.

Ralali moved to Bluegreen Office and had to restructuring Engineering teams. Here's the Website Performance Team.

Sometimes, I get chances to show on sharing knowledges to the Ralalians.

Thank you for experiences in these 2 years.
